name: Loving You
description: A long journey that creates a story. Two people who connect feelings, for the sake of the union of two interconnected hearts. The time will not be the same as the beginning of the meeting. The next step will be full of challenges. Readiness, maturity, mutual understanding open a beautiful story together. Joys and sorrows are passed together for the power of love that does not fade. Simple words but full of sincerity. I love you and will always love you.
